// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5942 — Mass File Rename (stormous)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9e8d4bbf-ab93-5022-9c04-3fe197198365

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
